title: Xbox Series S Revealed - Kinda Funny Games Daily 09.08.20
description:
The Xbox Series S is real! Let's talk about it!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:01:00 - Housekeeping
Kinda Hunnies return! This evening, we’re recording the Kinda Hunnies episode of the Kinda Funny Podcast! Get your questions in on patreon.com/kindafunny and look for the episode soon.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: 
Mohammed Mohammed, Tom Bock, Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:03:20 -  Xbox Series S Revealed Brad Sams
00:15:50 - Why did Microsoft reveal the XBox Series S in a tweet, despite the leak - Best Friends Q:BJ Bernardo
00:21:10 - Xbox’s monthly installments are a TERRIBLE deal! $25 dollars a month for 24 months (2 years) comes out to $600 for the Xbox Series S. What?!  - Best Friends Q:Aaron Sosa
00:26:38 - Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity Announced, Jeffy Grubb Grubb @ GamesBeat
00:31:50 - Do you think in years to come will we look back on 2020 as a good year for Nintendo fans? - Best Friends Q:Blockfighter
00:36:50 - EA Removes Ads from UFC 4, @ GameSpot 
00:42:44 - Kingdoms of Amalur Re-Reckoning Review Round-Up
00:49:20 - Colin Kaaepernick and Madden
00:51:20 - Out today
00:56:40 -  KF 
00:58:50 - Squad Up: Jordan Deeb
01:00:20 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Greg and Gary
